    </div>
    <p>
      git, npm, Docker, rez, VEX, MEL, ComfyUI, Qube, Davinci Resolve, Premiere
      Pro, Karma, Arnold, VRay, Renderman
    </p>
    <p>Leadership Initiative, Communication, Problem Solving</p>
